public class RhinoPageViewEvents static PageViewSpaceChange  (summary) (since) 5.0  Properties RhinoViewport ActiveViewport  (summary) The ActiveViewport is the same as the MainViewport for standard RhinoViews. In a RhinoPageView, the active viewport may be the RhinoViewport of a child detail object. Most of the time, you will use ActiveViewport unless you explicitly need to work with the main viewport. (since) 5.
